                                        <depth unit="cm"/>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </support>
                                <condition ana="#condition.complete"/>
		    </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout><p>Lines 1-3 are centred in the pediment. From line 4 onwards, the text is situated on the main rectangular body of the tablet. Lines 5-22 maintain a left-hand margin of one letter-space; line 4 begins hard against the left border fo the tablet. Line 23 (final line) is centred with larger letters (approximately double size).</p>
                                    <rs ana="#execution.engraved" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/3">engraved</rs>
